    <div class="container">
    <a name="anchor"></a>
      <!-- Block heading two -->
      <div class="block-heading-two">
        <h3><span>About Us</span></h3>
      </div>  
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-1">
          <p class="para-big">The founder of this application moved to Chicago by himself at the age of 25 to start a new life for himself. Within months, he lost his job and realized he was experiencing a hardship many Americans are facing today: unemployment.</p>
          <p>Although he had a college degree, he sent out over 50 applications a week with no luck for months. His biggest worry became wondering if he would have enough money for next month's rent. Most personal finance applications only showed him what he spent his money on, and he was left to plan his future income and expenses on his own. This adruous task was critical for making wise financial decisions and he spent an incredible amount of his time doing calculations and projections wondering where his finances stood. Luckily, he found a job just at the brink of going completely broke. Soon, he discovered his passion for coding and wanted his first app to help people all over the world solve this problem he struggled with. With this tool, he hopes to provide people all over the world with forecasts of their money so they can accurately plan and make wise financial decisions.</p>
          <br />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-1 text-center">
          <%= image_tag("quote.jpg") %>
        </div>
